  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of TTP054 for 12 Weeks in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Dose-Ranging, Parallel Group Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of TTP054 for 12 Weeks in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Inadequately Controlled on Metformin</official_title>
