  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of type 2 diabetes mellitus

          -  On a stable (for the last 3 months) regimen of either metformin alone or metformin in
             combination with one additional acceptable oral antidiabetic (OAD) agent

          -  HbA1c: Metformin only: 7.0 - 11.0%; Metformin + acceptable OAD agent: 6.5 - 9.5%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History or evidence of significant diabetic complications

          -  History of heart attack, stroke or congestive heart failure

          -  Severe, uncontrolled hypertension

          -  Frequent hypoglycemia

          -  Women of child-bearing potential
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
